    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "我母亲结婚三十年从没摘过婚戒。但尸体上没有戒指。",
    "enWords": "My mother never took off her wedding ring in thirty years of marriage. But there's no ring on the body.",
