    "cnWords": "搜证报告写得很清楚：废墟中没有任何与戒指相符的金属残留。尸体上没有，灰烬里也没有。",
    "enWords": "The search report is explicit: no metal remnants consistent with a ring were found. Not on the body, not in the ashes.",
